      \u201CUkko Nooa\u201D -melodian. Anna sormien etsi\xE4 oikea s\xE4vel: 1-1-1-3-2-2-2-4-3-3-2-2-1"
    englishInstruction: "Go to the view where the lower buttons are available. Press
      the buttons one by one and try different combinations until you recognize the
      \u201CUkko Nooa\u201D melody. Let your fingers find the correct tune: 1-1-1-3-2-2-2-4-3-3-2-2-1"
